document_data.mainbody:
el Suparra was a cultist and a member of the Knights of the Black Sword that arose in Caer-Dineval during the late 15 century DR.
Fel was tasked with guarding the gatehouse of the Caer, the eponymous castle of Caer-Dinveal. 
Fel worked alongside fellow cultist Huarwar Mulphoon.
